 Snow-filled experience<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Moon Peak Expedition<\/strong> \u2013 For seasoned climbers<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Dharamshala Culture Tour<\/strong> \u2013 Food, monasteries &amp; local life<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Whether you\u2019re a first-time trekker or an experienced mountaineer, <strong>Manu Adventures India<\/strong> offers expert-guided treks tailored to every traveler.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr \/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>2. Kashmir \u2013 The Timeless Paradise Rising Again<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/media1.thrillophilia.com\/filestore\/4eju2qn4hqxi5e6fq7esilpixebn_Downpic.cc-image430298721.jpg\" alt=\"A skier gliding down a snow-covered slope in Gulmarg, Kashmir, surrounded by tall pine trees and majestic Himalaya mountains under a clear winter sky.\" title=\"\"><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/pix10.agoda.net\/hotelImages\/4948199\/0\/44611f9ce1bad53b154ed11f237cf455.jpeg?ce=0&amp;s=1024x768\" alt=\"Traditional wooden houseboats floating on Dal Lake in Srinagar, Kashmir, with colorful shikaras and mountains in the background under a soft evening sky.\" title=\"\"><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>With tourism booming again, <strong>Kashmir<\/strong> is set to be one of India\u2019s top travel destinations in 2026. Its magical landscapes and serene beauty make it a year-round paradise.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Why Kashmir Is Trending<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Increasing popularity of winter tourism<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>New ski slopes and adventure sports<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Massive tourism improvement and safety<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Romantic, peaceful, and premium experiences<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Best Things to Do<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Stay in a <strong>Dal Lake houseboat<\/strong><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Skiing in <strong>Gulmarg<\/strong><\/li>\n\n